metadata.name: Advisor
metadata.description: Carbon12 is an ERC-20 token launched on December 23, 2022, focused on using the token and ecosystem as a tool for social impact in 12 main areas. The Carbon12 platform is built on trust, authenticity, and doing good using tokenomics which are wrapped into an ecosystem helping to transform the cryptoverse. When you join the Carbon12 ecosystem, you are joining something going beyond just a digital financial asset, but instead you are joining a movement to help deliver hope, abundance, and positive social impact around the world.
